    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "### Nested Loops\r\nDJ Mia is creating a track for a dance party. She coded this song, but she doesn't know how to use nested loops. Can you find the pattern in her code and use a **nested loop**? All of the blocks you'll need are already in the workspace!\r\n\r\nYou can use **pattern recognition** to help prepare for this level:\r\n- What parts of this song repeat? Can you identify it in the code?\r\n- Where do you see the same blocks used more than once?\r\n- Do any instruments or tracks create a repeating structure in this song?\r\n\r\n*Example code:* \r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/ad8d8aa22d106394280510c3b06a78e3-image-1750957993306.png)",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
